+    "# scipy.optimize\n",
+    "\n",
+    "Functions in the `optimize` module can be called by prepending them by `scipy.optimize.`. The module defines the following three functions:\n",
+    "\n",
+    "1. [scipy.optimize.bisect](#bisect)\n",
